Summary: Egg shaped object moved in straight line at same altitude into the horizon.
divs: Sighting Detailslying on bed watching TV. caught sight out of my eye. went over to the window and watched cross the sky.ballon at first until it moved west about 100mph at a constant altitude obviously not a ballon from this point. felt shocked and unrealistic. object continued until appeared out of sight.
